value.title: Fox News' Brit Hume begs Trump to not push through Ginsberg replacement before the election

Hume made the remarks on Fox News after noting that both President Donald Trump and Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell (R-KY) have previously vowed to hypothetically have a nominee approved before the election.
